{"title":"Fix: Deployment selector mismatch for vigil-app","body":"Root cause: Deployment selector mismatch between declared manifest (app: vigil-app-typo) and template labels (app: vigil-app), preventing immutable field update.

Evidence: Flux Kustomization error: "Deployment.apps \"vigil-app\" is invalid: [spec.template.metadata.labels: Invalid value: {\"app\":\"vigil-app\"}: `selector` does not match template `labels`, spec.selector: Invalid value: {\"matchLabels\":{\"app\":\"vigil-app-typo\"}}: field is immutable]"

This fix corrects the selector from `app: vigil-app-typo` to `app: vigil-app` to match the template labels, resolving the immutable field update issue."}
